    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment supports Accepted decision at Medium assurance for MRL 2. Six of seven assessed factors meet required levels. The discretization error factor achieved Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2; the team judged this one-step shortfall acceptable given conservative hemolysis model coefficients and the bounded operating envelope. All six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is fit for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
